		<title>Folge #80 &#8211; Geek-Week-Podcast: Google Knowledge Graph, Retina Display, Rundshow</title>
		<link>http://www.geek-week.de/2012/05/18/folge-80-geek-week-podcast-google-knowledge-graph-retina-display-rundshow/</link>
