		<title>Folge #65 &#8211; Geek-Week-Podcast: Sonos Play 3, Samwer, Google+, Facebook, Amazon</title>
		<link>http://www.geek-week.de/2011/12/24/folge-65-geek-week-podcast-sonos-play-3-samwer-google-facebook-amazon/</link>
